Hi Inclrs. We have a bunch of new features! Lock Password a new revamped Settings Menu recording in Albums and AR origin adjustments. In addition bug fixes for the camera locking and a whole variety have been completed. We apologise for the 2 month hiatus! We re back now!
HI Inclrs We fix the problems with sync this round and a few other quirks.

Hi Inclrs We have finally got Sync in Inclr! It s only v1.0 but its a big leap for us! Now you can sync your Inclrs across multiple devices! Qboard got some fixes too and a UI update with the menus. The Inclr Team
Hey Inclrs Sync is around the corner but this round we fixed from subscription issues. From the Inclr Team

Hi Inclrs In addition to our new World and AR views we fixed a few bugs this round especially some inherits from the new iOS. We also added new options for each view mode! For example add inclrs to an image like a masterplan. A new PDF viewer and a slew on new features compatible with iOS 11. Your Inclr Team.

Hi Inclrs We ve introduced two new exciting view modes: World View and Augmented Reality AR view. Get ready for a whole new dialogue using inclrs to describe your world. World View lets you place inclrs on a map. You can add travel inclrs or diary inclrs. Map out your projects around the world! Augmented Reality enters Inclr into a brave new 3D world. This is just the beginning. Inclr s founder is an architect so stay tune for a fuller set of AR features. Check it out today! From your Inclr team.
HI Inclrs we fixed a few bugs and we re working on sync. Not quite there yet tho.
Hey Inclrs We fixed some Qboard bugs and also introduced a 28 day Trial Version.
Hi Inclrs An upgraded Qboard and a new Album entry! Now you can add multiple photos to a single entry. Check it out! We also squashed a few bugs in this round.

Hi Inclrer We fixed the Queboard of bugs from our last update. We also got a cool new way to save things from the Web browser. Just hold and press on any element and it will give you options to save. Check it out!
Hi Inclrs We squashed more annoying bugs and improved the Queboard!

Hi Inclrs! We rehauled the Open In feature this round and made it a lot more robust. We also allow importing any kind of file into inclr now! That means you can really organise all your files with inclrs now.
Hi Inclrs! We found some bugs with importing files into Inclr and since squashed most of them. And we have a new feature to add content to Map pins! So have a go at logging your day on a map!

Hi fellow Inclrs. We are always improving Inclr! In this round we made massive improvements and fixed another series of annoying bugs. Once again we apologise the inconvenience. We also introduce Inclr Sets a new way to organise multiple sets of inclrs! Check out our new Document QR Scanner built right into the camera From the Inclr Team

Hi fellow Inclrs. We are always improving the Inclr Family. In this round we fixed quite a few bugs! Our bad! We also introduced adding Contents within Lists. Also introducing a speech feature that speaks while you navigate inclr! Great for driving. We also simplified Inclr s editing menus and added QR Code scanning. Check it out! From the Inclr Team
Hi fellow Inclrs. We ve put a lot of work into a major UI overhaul! All in the effort to make the experience more intuitive and simple. If you like it don t forget to let us know! From the Inclr Team

Hey there. We found a few bugs and have since squashed them. Nothing to worry about. Inclr Web has been out for a week and results are quite good. You can try it for free too! Inclr Launcher and Inclr Notes are going the club soon so stay tune.
Hi there we fixed a mistake on iPad inclrs showing too large on cloud search. We also squash a few more bugs.

Inclr is getting better and better with every version! The Grouping feature in the Map View now can be named with a title. You can search for backgrounds and logos using out built in Pexels and Google image search! Customising your inclr just got easier! We also fixed various naughty bugs as well as added a simple email sign in. Don t worry we don t use your email for anything other than to keep in touch with you. Keep the feedback coming and let us know if there s anything amiss. Thanks!

Hi Inclrs Today we are launching Inclr Web For Visual Bookmarking. We are trying to reach more users to take up the Inclr system so Inclr Web helps users store their web bookmarks using the Inclr way. Our team members use Inclr Web everyday. We hate bookmark lists and bars so for our daily web consumption Inclr Web is the answer. Check it out on the App Store! We also fixed some minor bugs relating to sign in emails. Oh and we have new graphics for the App Store. Let us know what you think! Yours Inclr Team.
